<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

	<head>

		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../iconfont/iconfont.css">

		<title>出错了！</title>

		<style>
			body{
				font-family: Adobe Heiti Std -WEBKIT-PICTOGRAPH,"microsoft yahei";
				font-size: 16px;
				background: #efefef;
				color: #666666;
			}
			body,ul,li,h1,p{
				list-style: none;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				font-weight: 100;
			}
			.text-center{
				text-align: center;
			}
			.content{
				background: url(../img/error-bg1.png) no-repeat;
				background-size: 100% auto;
				width: 54.5%;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding-top: 28%;
			}
			.content h1 span{
				display: inline-block;
				padding-left: 70px;
				background: url(../img/error-icon.png) no-repeat;
				background-size: auto 100%;
				background-position: left center;
				font-size: 36px;
				margin-bottom: 60px;
			}
			.content p{
				font-size: 16px;
				line-height: 40px;
				margin-bottom: 64px;
			}
			.content .action{
				padding-bottom:2.8%;
				background: url(../img/error-bg2.png) no-repeat;
				background-size: 100%;
				background-position: center bottom; 
			}
			.content ul{
				width: 410px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				overflow: hidden;
			}
			.content li{
				height: 110px;
				text-align: center;
				width: 50%;
				float: left;
				color: #000000;
				line-height: 40px;
				background: url(../img/error-bg3.png) no-repeat;
				background-size: 60%;
				background-position: center bottom; 
			}
			.content li i{
				vertical-align: middle;
				font-size: 30px;
				margin-right: 10px;
			}
		</style>

	</head>

	<body class="">
			<div class="content">
				<h1 class="text-center"><span>哎呀~  出错了！</span></h1>
				<p class="text-center">对于这个错误我们深感抱歉，我们会尽快解决这个问题～<br>您还可以点击它们</p>
				<div class="action">
					<ul>
						<li>
							<span><i class="iconfont icon-fanhuishouye"></i></span>
							返回首页
						</li>
						<li>
							<span><i class="iconfont icon-fanhuishangyibu"></i></span>
							返回上一页
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>	
	</body>

</html>